## 🔍 Architecture Validation Examples

### ✅ CORRECT Pattern:
```python
# Router (thin)
@router.post("/chat")
async def chat(request: ChatRequest) -> ChatResponse:
    result = await chat_service.process(request)
    return ChatResponse(**result)

# Service (thick)
class ChatService:
    async def process(self, request: ChatRequest) -> dict:
        # Business logic here
        return await self.lmstudio_client.chat(request)
```

### ❌ WRONG Pattern:
```python
# Router doing everything (violates layering)
@router.post("/chat")
async def chat(request: ChatRequest) -> ChatResponse:
    # ❌ Direct database call
    # ❌ Business logic in router
    # ❌ No service layer
    return ChatResponse(...)
```

