## 📚 Reference Architecture

**Current Stack:**
- FastAPI (async web framework)
- Pydantic (validation, settings)
- SQLAlchemy (ORM, async)
- Playwright (browser automation)
- LM Studio (local LLM)
- n8n/Node-RED (workflow integration)
- Apple Silicon M3 (hardware optimization)

**Layering:**
```
Client (n8n/Shortcuts/Python)
    ↓
Router (HTTP endpoints, validation)
    ↓
Service (business logic, orchestration)
    ↓
Module/Core (domain logic, utilities)
    ↓
External (LM Studio, Database, Browser)
```

